   <mods:abstract>Does not know the number or names of subscribers to the paper he left with
            Mr. Childs; would like twenty copies of the second volume when it is ready. Details his
            efforts to obtain extracts and translations of such Dutch manuscripts as might be
            interesting and useful to Belknap. Thanks him for the sermon; event shave and will
            verify the predictions of the Prophets. If these topics were more frequently discussed
            and understood, "there would probably be less Infidelity."</mods:abstract>
